      value: "\n\n\n\n\nthank you for playing\n\n\n\n\na special thank you to ram
        and sebastian lague and merge conflicts\n\n\n\nMohammad Shahroudi\r\nSounds,
        Back up Integrator, Tester/QA and Designer of the project\r\n\r\nCarson Cardoza
        \r\nPrimary Integrator\r\n\r\nDavid Martinez \r\nShop UI, Loading scene UI,
        and Plane Stats (currency, speed, damage, health)\r\n\r\nEric Rubio Salazer
        \r\n\r\nRhu Paatan\r\nMenu UI & General Menu Layouts, UI Asset Art, 3D Modelling,
        Sound Manager & Key Rebinding\r\n\r\nHector Rodriguez Duenas \r\nEnemy AI,
        Flight Controls, Ring Logic \r\n\r\nAlan Alvarez\r\nProcedural Terrain Generation,
        Day/Night System, Post-Processing Effects, Top-Down Map UI Display\r\n\r\ncredits
        here or something like that \r\n\r\n"
